author: Warhammer
description:
In the Helsmiths of Hashut battletome, there are three other shards of Hashut’s domain that are showcased. There’s the truly unique Ur-Zorn, the fiery Zharr Vyxa, and, finally, the dark and twisted Muspelzharr. Tune into this video to see Ollie show you how to paint each of them!
